query:
SELECT c.id as centreId, c.name as centreName, fl.id as floorId, fl.levelName, fl.mapImageUrl, fl.isHidden 
FROM shopping_centres c 
LEFT JOIN floor_levels fl ON fl.centreId = c.id 
WHERE c.name LIKE '%Highlands%';
